               <head xml:lang="en">Preparation</head>
               <desc xml:lang="en" type="definition">The preparation procedure consists of the
                  steps for effective recording of Raman spectra. These steps are: a) Positioning
                  the object/artwork, b) positioning the Raman instrument and c) Acquire of a high
                  resolution image of the cultural heritage object. The image will be used to
                  document the exact points that Raman analysis was performed.</desc>
